videos.description: Jay Huff denies Cassius Stanley and sets up Mamadi Diakite on the other end for the Virginia 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Huff's block sets up Diakite's trey ball) 2020/2/29

videos.headline: Huff's block sets up Diakite's trey ball

videos.description: Virginia breaks the full-court press against Duke, setting up the wide open alley-oop jam for Jay Huff.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Woldetensae lobs it to Huff for the two-handed slam) 2020/2/29

videos.headline: Woldetensae lobs it to Huff for the two-handed slam

videos.description: Duke's Vernon Carey Jr. spins past his defender and finishes with the left-handed layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Carey spins to a left-handed finish) 2020/2/29

videos.headline: Carey spins to a left-handed finish

videos.description: Virginia's Jay Huff is on fire as he slams down back-to-back electric dunks against Duke.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Huff drops back-to-back hammers on Duke) 2020/2/29

videos.headline: Huff drops back-to-back hammers on Duke

videos.description: Javin DeLaurier fails to finish the play and misses the would-be slam dunk against Virginia.

videos.headline: DeLaurier miscues the would-be slam dunk

videos.description: Duke's Tre Jones finds Cassius Stanley on the leak out for the two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Stanley gets the fast-break slam on Virginia) 2020/2/29

videos.headline: Stanley gets the fast-break slam on Virginia

videos.description: Jay Huff gets the rebound in traffic and manages to throw down a reverse slam dunk.
videos.headline: Huff rattles the rim with reverse jam

videos.description: Mamadi Diakite goes up for a block but gets called for goaltending late against Duke.
videos.headline: Duke takes late lead on goaltending call

videos.description: Jay Huff is hyped after he gets the clutch block on Vernon Carey Jr. to prevent Duke from going ahead late.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Huff fired up after clutch block on Duke in final seconds) 2020/2/29

videos.headline: Huff fired up after clutch block on Duke in final seconds

videos.description: Jay Huff flirts with a triple-double, scoring 15 points, blocking 10 shots and collecting 9 rebounds as Virginia takes down No. 7 Duke 52-50.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Huff’s clutch block, big dunks fuel UVA to upset of No. 7 Duke) 2020/2/29 ESHEET SOTFULL
